data.description: Start the new year out with this move in ready home!!  This is an incredible opportunity in the heart of North Raleigh's Dominion Park!  A meticulously maintained 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom cul-de-sac fenced home is a true gem. Situated in a prime location with easy access to the 540 highway, this home boasts convenience like no other. It's centrally located, providing swift access to all the Triangle has to offer. Step inside and you'll immediately notice the spaciousness and natural light that permeates every room. The generous primary suite is a haven of tranquility, featuring an oversized closet and a newly tiled bathroom floor and shower, giving it a fresh, modern touch. The bonus room is versatile, offering the potential for a large 5th bedroom or a fantastic entertainment space. The kitchen is a true focal point, with granite countertops, a tile backsplash, and a convenient butler's pantry. Roof (2014). For those outdoor enthusiasts, Umstead Park is only 6miles away.
